Michel Gill https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michel_Gill 0 Michel Gill (born April 16, 1960), also known as Michael Gill, is an American actor best known for playing President Garrett Walker in the Netflix series House of Cards and Gideon Goddard on Mr. Robot.
